title: The Anthony Cumia Show 10-10-16
description:
I wrote a tool that rips anything on the Cumia site and sends it through ffmpeg without interaction.

Testing waters with the 10-10-16 Dipaolo show in 720p. I also have all Connectpal podcasts and Sirius and all Artie Lange Uncensored stuff.

I'll stop seeding within 48 hours sometime unless I can get some support through bitcoin(other people need to seed). Send To: 1AFiKbmRUyagA2Su812YFwtap4w2w5npdE

If I can get donations at a certain rate I'll put up a 24/7 seed server and put stuff up in real-time. I can get other stuff too; I write all my own tools to auto-rip.

I'd like to do it all daily but the time and subscriptions all cost money and I can't sit snd do this. I can auto-rip Stern off Sirius too every day
